Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在巴黎万国博览会上相识的 强、娜蒂亚与大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭到企图夺取神秘宝石 『蔚蓝之水』的邪恶三人组袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强驾驶他发明的飞机 勉强脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后经历了重重冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们迫降在某座岛屿上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到那里竟是神秘组织 『新亚特兰提斯』的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们在岛上认识了 一名小女孩 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然而玛莉、大王与娜蒂亚 却不幸落入新亚特兰提斯手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一名戴着面具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,名叫『石像鬼』的男子 不但尊称娜蒂亚为公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还带她参观了杀人武器 『巴别塔』的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其威力强大到能轻易摧毁 海上的小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 那座秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也由于再度碰面的三人组与强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及尼莫船长所率领的万能潜水艇 鹦鹉螺号大显神威
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因而毁于一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:27.16,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#09 尼莫的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被抓起来的人们 不知道有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家好像都逃到海边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说石像鬼那伙人都逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在摸什么鱼 快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不但被打得伤痕累累 而且还进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再这样下去我的葛兰坦会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 为了帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害我都感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 向鹦鹉螺号求救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是曾经帮过我们的 那艘潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收到刚才那台奇怪的坦克 所发出的求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,念出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『求救 求救 葛兰迪丝』 内容如上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问该怎么处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们也曾和 新亚特兰提斯对抗过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总不能见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方愿意帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真走运！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又可以搭上那艘船了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要搭上那艘船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大的船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 有够大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到这种巨大潜水艇 已经建造成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又能搭上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？看你闷闷不乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不喜欢这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将收容各位至后部停机库 请绕到舰尾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关起来 快关紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遇难者收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 损害报告已经汇整完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,外廓只有轻微受损
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 氢原子传导管 与磁场调整装置严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,修理需要多少时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,48个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能缩短吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为专家的轮机长 既然说需要48个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就表示必须花上48个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰内的所有能源 已经切换成电池供给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么一来 行动也受到相当大的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很明白你已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们只能祈祷 不会发生什么意外事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就有劳你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 让石像鬼脱逃 我感到十分遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会死心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不能死心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全体船员也都抱持着这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来 要怎么安置那台怪坦克里的成员？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若有伤患或是病人 就给予最大的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这件事就交给你来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『不能让身分不明人士 在船内游荡』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『一旦坦克修理完毕』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『就提供充足的水与粮食 请他们离开』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说的没错吧 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这群人懂不懂礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用缆绳吊起凯撒琳之后 居然就自己先跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是很感谢他们肯伸出援手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这艘船真让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们到底是在高兴什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都没用到铆钉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是怎么让船身密合的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很厉害对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船可说是未来科学的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然有机会搭上 这么了不起的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 之前会自动打开喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎各位来到本船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贵船愿意伸出援手 我们诚心感激 这位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来为你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位是我的助手 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,助…助手？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那位女性是 葛兰迪丝·格兰帕小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是我俩的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而在下名为桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后还请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着对那种不敢露出 真面目的女人报上自己名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是 是我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我名叫艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,担任这艘船的副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见 强 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到还有机会再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她叫作玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我们在岛上认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的双亲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被新亚特兰提斯那伙人给…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从现在起 本船将会保护各位的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不允许各位 在船舰内擅自走动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我将会为各位准备 必需品及住房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 感冒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为一直被关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上去请医生过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那石像鬼是因为认识你 才会说出那种话啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 而且他还称那座玻璃塔 为『巴别塔』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴别塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是在旧约圣经里 提到的那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这我就不晓得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 他一直在说山铜什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山铜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是指塔下方那些大玻璃板吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道为什么 那跟『蔚蓝之水』挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水与新亚特兰提斯之间 一定存在着什么秘密关联
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有 跟这艘鹦鹉螺号也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 有办法打开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 这好像是用电力 还是磁力上锁的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真了不起的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠发夹根本动不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回就交给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟这里的墙壁实在太坚固了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的手都变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里的医生说她只是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我们去探病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很简单 拜托人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正一定有人 正在监听这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 我们想去找大姐头 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是她有个万一 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为药效她才会睡得那么熟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天就会痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不到一天就能将感冒治好？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了不起 这是魔法药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是科学的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是一艘惊人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长 修理进展得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船体的修理 到早上应该就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有拦截到 新亚特兰提斯的通讯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使失去一两个前进基地 他也不会感到惊慌是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 你还是回房休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我要待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『全体船员都在不眠不休地赶工』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『不能只有我去睡觉』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长 你话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然如此 我就再多说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们又收容到那些孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是制作了 那架飞机的孩子们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早知道那里是石像鬼的基地 我就不会让他们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我对那些孩子感到过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次你还是不打算 与他们见面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我接下来会到哪里去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船体已经修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了 稍微去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有 葛兰迪丝小姐 听说已经醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说是奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得挺腥的 味道好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们说这非常有营养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么的奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是鲸鱼奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲸鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然让我喝这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再怎么说我可都是 格兰家的独生女 怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰了 现在方便吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉现在才来和各位见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是这艘船的船长 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坐着听我说就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问你身体还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个…托你的福 我已经好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊…那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本船会将几位的交通工具修好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,修理完后 几位就能随时启程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我们会自己将它修好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 那我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个…请再说一次你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫 失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫…尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,症状的确不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 错不了 就是那个老毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真拿大姐头没辄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一见到沧桑的中年男人 就会马上变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种中年男人哪里好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 还是快点将葛兰坦修好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还用得着说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要尽快离开这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离开？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 要让大姐头离开 那个中年男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船的科学技术 有许多值得学习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就我观察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船跟那个叫石像鬼的家伙 是敌我关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待在这种船上 命再多条都不够用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…艾丽朵拉人也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只要一遇到美人 就会无条件心软
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪…哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说大姐头跟艾丽朵拉 哪个重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你该不会要说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你会协助我的脱离计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就此定案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始吧 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还是去探望一下 葛兰迪丝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森与韩森其实人都不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为有那三个人的协助 我才能顺利将你们救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得他们为什么会帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们想要的是蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是为了想得到它 才对我们伸出援手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我跟他们在一起的时候 蔚蓝之水都没发光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是它故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想应该不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也许是它要在我身上 才会发光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把嘴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 已经肿成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要带它去看医生 妈妈都是那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对 玛莉 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们马上出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还能顺便探望葛兰迪丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是带大王去看病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论如何都要说服大姐头 离开这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正就只有两条老路 不是大姐头自己死心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是被那个中年男人甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论怎样 这都是场没有结果的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然这样 还不如早点死心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狮子感冒不会传染给人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们怎么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王好像感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顺便来看看葛兰迪丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可就多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 可以稍等一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们有要紧的事 要和大姐头谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太自私了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 蔚蓝之水并没有发光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定是因为 葛兰迪丝不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强、娜蒂亚 我们大家都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很抱歉之前把你追得到处逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是你用不着再担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我决定暂时留在这艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么各位 我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看这情况…她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 韩森 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖 没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 大王 医生说你很快就会康复的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 怎么大伙都出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来得正好 我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他就是那位少年 强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初…初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你的帮助 尼莫舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫强是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要叫我舰长 这艘船并不是军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…对不起 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 这边几位是 玛莉与名叫大王的狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不准擅自在船内走动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他那个人跟我想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长好有男人味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真正的海上男儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你不那么认为吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:20:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也感冒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 不是的 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事的 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了 那是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是管风琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你怎么会跑来这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我听到这首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就觉得是妈妈在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,振作点 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在弹琴的人是尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 这里是尼莫船长的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有人能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:54.81,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:24:02.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:08.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:12.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:21.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:31.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.53,0:24:40.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.27,0:24:44.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:49.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.28,0:24:58.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.23,0:25:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被命令搬离你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.87,0:25:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.23,0:25:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.23,0:25:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们说男生和女生共处一室 怕会发生不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.24,0:25:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你脸怎么红成那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.78,0:25:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好下流 思想真污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.81,0:25:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是啦 我才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.51,0:25:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『葛兰坦的活跃』
